items.headline: Welcome to the Meghan Trainor Wiki!
items.desc: The Meghan Trainor Wiki is the official wiki for the american singer, Meghan Trainor. This wiki has every bit of information about Meghan. We are trying to make this a big wiki so we would love some help around the wiki and you could be doing us a big favour!
